## Installation instructions ##

Copy the files 'any2vob' & 'any2dvd' into your $PATH somewhere.

Example:
'/usr/bin' or '/usr/local/bin'

any2vob - Encodes the movies
any2dvd - Calls on any2vob to encode the movies, then creates the DVD menus & burns to DVD

After installation, type `any2dvd -h` for a help page.
Any2vob can be used as a standalone tool seperate from any2dvd, for creation of .VOB files only, type `any2vob -h` for a help page.
